{"tid":840771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英航員工轟賠償不合理","createTime":"2018-09-29T05:20:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T03:25:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7a8080240637ddb72405d57dff4247e705beb0b2","tid":840771,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:20:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180929/20510804\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180929%2F20510804&d=F9r2SQMCT6%2FOx%2BzmKK%2FXAHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=642e2ff6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180929%2F20510804&h=a79d67b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180929/20510804</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年09月29日 <br />\n<br />\n英航員工轟賠償不合理<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180929/large/29la9p04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180929%2Flarge%2F29la9p04.jpg&h=04115c60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英航員工等人昨圍繞英航櫃位叫口號示威。朱家駿攝 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】早前英航向員工宣佈在下月31日結束香港基地，全部85名員工被即時終止合約。職工盟和英航香港機艙服務員工會等約30人昨晚在機場抗議，批評公司的賠償方案違反本地勞工法例，要求立即與員工商討合理方案。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n高呼「英航無良　白做一場」<br />\n<br />\n英航員工、職工盟秘書長李卓人、小麗民主教室劉小麗和公民黨譚民豪等30人圍繞英航櫃位高呼「英航無良，白做一場」口號示威，更有員工宣讀自創的臨別機艙宣言時一度感觸落淚。<br />\n<br />\n英航工會總幹事吳敏兒表示，公司所提供的賠償方案，沒有詳細列明計算方式，只是提供一個金額。他們經計算後，發現代通知金以基本月薪計算，「有同期職級相同嘅員工賠償金額竟然都相差幾萬蚊」。她指，勞工處職員向工會表示，公司給予的津貼也屬於月薪，因此只以基本月薪來計算代通知金是不符香港的勞工法例。<br />\n<br />\n吳敏兒表示，工會曾3次要求與管理層會面，惟對方以忙碌為由拒絕。她指出，工會的55個會員不會簽署「唔清唔楚」的賠償文件，工會亦已發律師信要求公司就回覆文件的期限延長60日，以讓他們了解文件中細則。<br />\n<br />\n■記者李思潁  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n兔唇女童受虐　7℃捱餓沖凍水涼　 待遇與妹差天共地　偏心父母候判<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n兩女網售月餅券騙財被捕"},{"pid":"cb40409498c4e3b6d7ea57c4c51956252b8e2034","tid":840771,"uid":35815,"like":2,"dislike":14,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T07:32:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"81e783f4a5634556c4b1f9c738f2bdb811ffe394","tid":840771,"uid":35815,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T07:34:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c1ca248ff5872298b4444ae63661a5536347afbf","tid":840771,"uid":35815,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T07:35:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b50fd0260c2e133a04c5030541418786c1e105f2","tid":840771,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T01:43:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"62f73c4054a0f40151830cb9b899d804d5b16f07","tid":840771,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T01:45:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 垃圾"},{"pid":"eace3b549554932a71ae197ab15c499b132b681a","tid":840771,"uid":62668,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T01:47:19.000Z","msg":"全部都係垃圾 <br />\n一早應該炒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64b5db359ada666e36e83502c4880c9b52e52934","tid":840771,"uid":3482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T02:05:14.000Z","msg":"小麗老母又黎抽水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4002a8c0983b6e5e39480672b5113f9c14d08df","tid":840771,"uid":28279,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T02:10:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連登仔個個唔憂打工，呢幾年經濟又好<br />\n唔明老闆執咗間寫字樓走佬，打工仔係幾咁徬徨，董建華年代成日見<br />\n啲公司係可以所有賠償計錯哂，無負責人出嚟同你傾任何嘢，工又突然無咗，樓又仲供緊"},{"pid":"c9f7ddec08da1c539bea28f57fd2a533ddde3c3e","tid":840771,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T02:13:25.000Z","msg":"仆街鬼佬又蝦我地，屌你老母"},{"pid":"f9dff9c40d17ead73db1dbb5fde7882d163719ca","tid":840771,"uid":35815,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"